query:
SELECT v.id, v.formandoId, v.eventoId, v.valorTotal, v.status, 
       FROM_UNIXTIME(v.createdAt / 1000) as data_venda,
       f.nome as formando_nome, f.turmaId 
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id 
WHERE YEAR(FROM_UNIXTIME(v.createdAt / 1000)) = 2026 
  AND MONTH(FROM_UNIXTIME(v.createdAt / 1000)) = 6
ORDER BY v.createdAt
